OL,3,CNurses in NI warn declining staff
OL,4,Cnumbers threaten patient safety
OL,6,FNurses in Northern Ireland are warning
OL,7,Fthat a decline in numbers and rising
OL,8,Fclinical complexities are threatening
OL,9,Fpatient safety.
OL,11,FA survey carried out by The Royal
OL,12,FCollege of Nursing asked more than
OL,13,F13,000 staff about their experiences
OL,14,Fon their most recent shift.
OL,16,FOnly one in 10 here said staffing was
OL,17,Fat the right level for all patient
OL,18,Fneeds to be met.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
