OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779293476
OL,3,CNurses in NI warn declining staff
OL,4,Cnumbers threaten patient safety
OL,6,FA quarter of nursing staff say
OL,7,Fregistered nurse numbers are so far
OL,8,Fbelow what is required that there is
OL,9,Fnow a 'high risk' of harm on shift.
OL,11,FIn Northern Ireland, three in four
OL,12,F(75%) felt emotionally exhausted on
OL,13,Ftheir last shift. Reports of
OL,14,Fexhaustion were highest among those
OL,15,Fwho said their shift was understaffed.
OL,17,FAdditionally, four fifths of nurses
OL,18,F(80%) say that clinical complexity has
OL,19,Fincreased over the last two years
OL,20,Falone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
