OL,3,CNurses in NI warn declining staff
OL,4,Cnumbers threaten patient safety
OL,6,FMore than two thirds (68%) say the
OL,7,Fsituation is now forcing them to make
OL,8,Fdifficult decisions about prioritising
OL,9,Fcare.
OL,11,FNursing staff across all NHS and HSC
OL,12,Fsettings say adults, children and
OL,13,Fthose with mental ill health are all
OL,14,Fpresenting with more clinical
OL,15,Fcomplexity which is placing
OL,16,Funsustainable pressure on staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
