OL,3,CNurses in NI warn declining staff
OL,4,Cnumbers threaten patient safety
OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV, RCN Northern Ireland
OL,7,FExecutive Director, Professor Rita
OL,8,FDevlin said: "The general public will
OL,9,Fknow if anybody has been in hospital
OL,10,Frecently or cared for in the
OL,11,Fcommunity, the number of extra
OL,12,Fpatients that have been put in
OL,13,Fcorridor beds, in the wards, in the ED
OL,14,Fdepartments, and the case load of
OL,15,Fpatients being looked after in
OL,16,Fcommunity is just growing."
OL,18,FThe Department of Health said it
OL,19,Frecognises that reform cannot be
OL,20,Fdelivered without supporting the
OL,21,Fworkforce and focusing on retention.
OL,26,@pD@NOU
